[{"id":1135227,"node":"推广","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/promotions","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_mini.png?m=1658911802","description":"<p>现在人与人之间的信任很难建立，我在 V 站买过好物，深知信任不易，最近在论坛看到有朋友在讨论茶叶，特来分享一下自家的茶叶，欢迎大家试试看，期待听到反馈，明年还能再来！</p>\n<ul>\n<li>茶叶名称：霍山黄芽 见<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%9C%8D%E5%B1%B1%E9%BB%84%E8%8A%BD\" rel=\"nofollow\">百度百科</a>，品质上更为接近绿茶。</li>\n<li>茶叶简介：采用闷黄工艺，咖啡碱和茶多酚含量相对较高，适合在学习、加班或待客时饮用，能帮助提神、集中注意力。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>重点：抽奖细则说明</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>抽奖数量：共 12 份，谷雨前茶叶 1 罐，装满约 125g （罐尺寸约 12×8×12cm ）</li>\n<li>截止时间：2025.06.01 16:00:00 （端午节期间称量、打包、发货）</li>\n<li>抽奖算法：写了个 <a href=\"https://greasyfork.org/zh-CN/scripts/537604-v2ex-random-floor\" rel=\"nofollow\">V2EX 抽奖的油猴脚本</a>，楼层去重后通过脚本抽取，随机数种子为 md5(截止时间之前的总楼层数)。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img alt=\"快速展示\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.v2ex.co/05P6MS4Jl.png\"/></p>\n<h2>茶园故事：七年的试错与漫长等待</h2>\n<p>父亲是个闲不下来的人，一辈子都在忙活。七年前，承包了荒地，种香椿、中药、茶叶等，大多折腾了个寂寞。</p>\n<p>唯独这片茶园没有辜负付出，依山傍水、阳光充足、纯天然无污染，在等待中迎来了回报。<a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/PFZeDHAdRhpiJMG27\" rel=\"nofollow\">查看茶园在谷歌地图中的位置</a></p>\n<p><img alt=\"故事发展\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.v2ex.co/a69OtA59.jpeg\"/></p>\n<p>从地图能看出，茶园在大别山深处，去县城需要 2 个多小时。前几年茶季，每天夜里炒茶，凌晨跑市场，好在茶叶品质不错，总能早早卖出，慢慢地，也有了固定的收购商和回头客，虽说如今少了奔波，但缺乏直销渠道，利润微薄。</p>\n<p>如果风调雨顺，明年的产量还会进一步提高。可岁月不等人，父亲生产销售两头抓，已渐感力不从心。</p>\n<p>我也尝过不少茶，感觉父亲的茶挺好，陪我度过无数加班的夜，身边朋友们评价也都不错。最近在论坛看见不少茶友，想试试看大家对茶叶的评价，赞美和批评都欢迎。如果反馈还行，我想投资一些，给它申请个小品牌，做些包装，明年再试着上电商平台推广。</p>\n<h2>广告时间：茶叶怎么卖</h2>\n<p>目前选的这两款茶叶产量高，品质好，价格实惠，适合做为口粮茶或招待客人。</p>\n<p>下面是具体价格，含运费，v2 的每一份快递会准备 10g 左右试喝小包，如果不合口味，可以随时退货。目前有两种渠道购买：</p>\n<p>一、扫码进入拼多多店铺，联系客服输入 V2EX 或 v 站，会送一张<strong>50 的券</strong>，再下单购买（因怕别人误拍，没那么多货，抵用后与下表相同）。\n二、扫右侧添加我夫人的微信，由她负责客服与售后。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"产品价格\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.v2ex.co/164W8Rm2.png\"/></p>\n<h2>致谢</h2>\n<p>感谢你读到这里。山高路远，如果有机会，欢迎来坐坐，喝杯茶、看看山。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135227","replies":419,"created_ts":1748507723,"created":"16:35:23","title":"[抽奖] 送 12 份自家茶叶 - 推广下自家茶园与两款口粮茶","author":"vace","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/vace","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/871a/3741/174366_mini.png?m=1748505063"},{"id":1135041,"node":"汽车","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/car","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960","description":"蔚来 et5t 颜值在线，优惠下来 27 万，车子各方面很智能，现在还可以租电，价格直接来到了 20 万面料做工都很不错<br /><br />毛豆 y 优惠下来 24 万左右，试驾过一次，感觉没有毛豆 3 好开，除了品牌效应，空间大，其他方面好像没有什么吸引我的地方<br /><br />比较纠结。。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135041","replies":136,"created_ts":1748479654,"created":"08:47:34","title":"第二辆车，考虑电车，特斯拉 Y 还是微辣 ET5t","author":"Apple2023","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Apple2023","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/54c4/8265/495791_mini.png?m=1732242867"},{"id":1135205,"node":"汽车","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/car","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960","description":"<p>接上一篇帖子( <a href=\"https://v2ex.com/t/1128701\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://v2ex.com/t/1128701</a>)  经过一番对比后，最终还是选择了自己喜欢的君越艾维亚，20.5w 落地。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529143424486\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/WY8sou.png\"/></p>\n<h2>提车</h2>\n<p>加满第一箱油🤓\n<img alt=\"image-20250529144412015\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/3WMt5j.png\"/></p>\n<p>再拍一组车的内饰照片🥰</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529144835512\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/CF4LEp.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529144853987\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/9YqdlU.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529144907684\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/VtyiCh.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529144922728\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/4VEpyQ.png\"/></p>\n<h2>地下车库</h2>\n<p>挂好牌子，在小区物业做了登记，车终于停到地下车库了。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529145503533\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/E8jgUg.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529145520053\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/xoN8vX.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529145535820\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/oJq7IB.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529145549429\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/5DjHpI.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529151600234\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/e8jWkw.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529145709143\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/3P0daF.png\"/></p>\n<h2>贴车衣发现车子被划</h2>\n<p>在地库停了 2 天后，时间也来到了周五，我把车开到了朋友推荐的店贴车衣。周六一大早，老板开工时发现车子的后备箱位置有划痕，拍照给我看了，我想着都大老远从佛山开到深圳来了，就让老板给我做了修复（老板人比较好，给我免费修复了）。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529152250655\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/neJwQa.png\"/></p>\n<h2>联系物业</h2>\n<p>车衣贴好后，我回到了佛山，开始复盘车子是什么时候被划的。翻出了我停地库时拍的照片，正好有拍到后备箱位置的照片，可以清晰的看出是没有划痕的，于是我就找物业要说法了。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529151653422\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/aEvxFE.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529150754713\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/shGGsy.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529150840697\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/I7zhkc.png\"/></p>\n<p>到了晚上我问了她结果。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529150956277\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/7d4Ie5.png\"/></p>\n<p>无奈，只能等他们慢慢查了（截止发帖，物业也没给我结果）。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image-20250529151055825\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://resource.kaisir.cn/uploads/MarkDownImg/20250529/vVTjKZ.png\"/></p>\n<h2>事后复盘</h2>\n<p>这次也怪我没有第一时间发现这条划痕，以后开车前我就先绕圈一周，发现车子被破坏，立马报警，让警察来处理此事。</p>\n<p>这次的事情，大概率是不了了之了（心疼我的新车啊🥹）</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135205","replies":126,"created_ts":1748503423,"created":"15:23:43","title":"好消息：提车了 坏消息：被人恶意划了🤬","author":"BaymaxK","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/BaymaxK","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c735/cd24/538620_mini.png?m=1741015795"},{"id":1135198,"node":"微信","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/wechat","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/55b3/7c5c/649_mini.png?m=1651386010","description":"我们帮很多培训机构开发公众号/服务号的功能，其中有一项学员人人都需要的“课程提醒”通知腾讯永远不批准相关的模版通知模版，非要我们改成订阅通知。问题是很多会员不需要经常进页面去同意订阅通知，时而能发时而不能发更麻烦，会导致更多纠纷。而且滑稽的是，预约、取消课程的通知又是可以发的。还有很多其他的无关紧要的通知也可以发。偏偏上课提醒这种强需求不能发<br /><br />如果用户觉得会被打扰，他取消关注不就得了。为什么非要喂用户“订阅通知”这种💩呀！","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135198","replies":126,"created_ts":1748503012,"created":"15:16:52","title":"腾讯确实是一家很傲慢的公司","author":"Radeon","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Radeon","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/63f6/019c/26842_mini.png?m=1730423863"},{"id":1135042,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195","description":"<p>秒：10000000000\n毫秒：10000000000000\n时区：Asia/Shanghai\nGMT：Sun Nov 21 2286 01:46:40 GMT+0800</p>\n<p>对各位写的代码有影响吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135042","replies":117,"created_ts":1748479983,"created":"08:53:03","title":"到上海时间 2286 年 11 月 21 日 01:46:40，秒级的时间戳到 11 位，对各位写的代码有影响吗","author":"zxcjqyy","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zxcjqyy","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7ca/c1af/392390_mini.png?m=1552964050"},{"id":1135164,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1739135407","description":"我和老婆对话会用到“帮”字，1. 我帮你带娃 2. 我帮你打扫卫生 3.生活中我和她对话只要当前从他手上接过的事我都会说“我帮你”<br />我老婆会很不高兴，说这个是我们两一起的事，为什么是帮我，你本来就有部分责任，不要说帮。但是我认为这个只是一个行为动词，没有说这些责任全是我老婆的意思，也没有“施舍”的意思（没想到好的词描述）。<br />由于我屡次不改吵了一架（语言习惯还真不好改），想咨询一下各位对“帮”字的看法，是倾向我还是我老婆","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135164","replies":101,"created_ts":1748498848,"created":"14:07:28","title":"由于“我帮你”和老婆吵了一架，想问问各位的看法","author":"eipi1","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/eipi1","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/af70b0566d7acc3c51a9863c5133abe8?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":1135063,"node":"重庆","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/chongqing","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c16a/5320/31_mini.png?m=1584298370","description":"坐标某直辖市，想请教一下大家对停车收费问题的处理方式。<br /><br />目前工作地点所在的地下车库必须包月停车，且名额有限，还需要抢位。<br />楼下的停车只能停在路边划线区域，每天如果按规定缴费，大概要 20 多元，而且没有“12 小时内封顶”的优惠。如果加班的话，费用轻轻松松就接近 30 元了。<br />因此，我平时一般都是停完车就直接走人，并不主动缴费。<br /><br />昨天发生了一件事让我有些疑惑：刚下车，负责收费的工作人员就过来让我补交之前的停车费。他还出示了相关文件，说是国家层面的规定，还提到了重庆发改委 2022 年 1 号文件。<br />我本来也不想和一线工作人员起冲突，既然对方拿出了文件，我也就象征性地缴了一部分，最后几笔加起来一共付了 100 多元。<br /><br />所以想来论坛请教一下：<br />像这种路边停车没交费的情况，你们是怎么处理的？<br />是坚持不交，还是会和工作人员“协调”一下？<br />如果长期不交，会不会有实际的后果，比如被追缴、列入黑名单、影响征信之类的？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135063","replies":96,"created_ts":1748482542,"created":"09:35:42","title":"路边停车，各位都是如何应对的？","author":"hytex","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hytex","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/bf0c04bf5f1863642d80f945d46cd413?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":1135050,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135050","replies":86,"created_ts":1748480644,"created":"09:04:04","title":"友友们， M4 Macbook Air 13 寸， 32G+256G 这配置干后端开发是不是能战五年？","author":"Jiangyf","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Jiangyf","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/df46/4644/346112_mini.png?m=1658667433"},{"id":1135100,"node":"广州","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/guangzhou","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_mini.png?m=1542423096","description":"<p>想买九号的 FZ110 ，广州要 4799 ，北京只要 4199 搞不懂</p>\n<p>等了大半个月的 618 ，也没有降一点价格，618 到底有没有优惠啊电鸡  </p>\n<p>有没有知道的大佬来说下。</p>\n<p>需求：一家三口周边出行，所以缓震和续航要好点的。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1135100","replies":75,"created_ts":1748486899,"created":"10:48:19","title":"广州买哪个牌子电鸡性价比高","author":"edward1987","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/edward1987","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1aac/352c/563796_mini.png?m=1653449106"},{"id":1135037,"node":"Rust","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/rust","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2dac/e78f/790_mini.png?m=1632977380","descriptio